            <h3 style="margin-top: 20px;">üìä Session Stats</h3>
            <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #ffffff 100%); padding: 15px; border-radius: 10px;">
                <div class="stats-item">
                    <span>Tools used:</span>
